{
 "cells": [
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "# Generate 1D-2D contacts\n",
    "\n",
    "This is a basic introduction for generating contacts with meshkernel"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 1,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [
    {
     "data": {
      "text/plain": [
       "'7.0.4'"
      ]
     },
     "execution_count": 1,
     "metadata": {},
     "output_type": "execute_result"
    }
   ],
   "source": [
    "from meshkernel import MakeGridParameters, Mesh1d, Mesh2d, MeshKernel, GeometryList\n",
    "from meshkernel.version import __version__\n",
    "\n",
    "__version__"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "Other imports"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 2,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "import numpy as np\n",
    "from pathlib import Path\n",
    "import matplotlib.pyplot as plt"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 3,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "def plot_mesh_and_contacts(mesh1d_output_0, mesh2d_output_0, contacts_output_0=None):\n",
    "    fig, ax = plt.subplots()\n",
    "    mesh1d_output_0.plot_edges(ax, color=\"blue\")\n",
    "    mesh2d_output_0.plot_edges(ax, color=\"black\")\n",
    "    if contacts_output_0:\n",
    "        contacts_output_0.plot_edges(ax, mesh1d_output_0, mesh2d_output_0, color=\"red\")\n",
    "    ax.plot(\n",
    "        mesh1d_output_0.node_x, mesh1d_output_0.node_y, \"o\", color=\"blue\", markersize=5\n",
    "    )\n",
    "    plt.show()"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "# Set mesh2d and mesh 1d"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 4,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "# create base grid\n",
    "mk = MeshKernel()\n",
    "\n",
    "make_grid_parameters = MakeGridParameters(\n",
    "    angle=0,\n",
    "    origin_x=0.0,\n",
    "    origin_y=0.0,\n",
    "    upper_right_x=100.0,\n",
    "    upper_right_y=100.0,\n",
    "    block_size_x=10.0,\n",
    "    block_size_y=10.0,\n",
    ")\n",
    "\n",
    "mk.curvilinear_compute_rectangular_grid_on_extension(make_grid_parameters)\n",
    "mk.curvilinear_convert_to_mesh2d()\n",
    "\n",
    "mesh1d_node_x = [0.0, 50.0, 100.0]\n",
    "mesh1d_node_y = [20.0, 20.0, 20.0]\n",
    "mesh1d_edge_nodes = [0, 1, 1, 2]\n",
    "mesh1d = Mesh1d(\n",
    "    node_x=mesh1d_node_x, node_y=mesh1d_node_y, edge_nodes=mesh1d_edge_nodes\n",
    ")\n",
    "mk.mesh1d_set(mesh1d)"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 5,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [
    {
     "data": {
      "image/png": "",
      "text/plain": [
       "<Figure size 640x480 with 1 Axes>"
      ]
     },
     "metadata": {},
     "output_type": "display_data"
    }
   ],
   "source": [
    "mesh1d_output_0 = mk.mesh1d_get()\n",
    "mesh2d_output_0 = mk.mesh2d_get()\n",
    "contacts_output_0 = mk.contacts_get()\n",
    "plot_mesh_and_contacts(mesh1d_output_0, mesh2d_output_0, contacts_output_0)"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "## Compute contacts"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 6,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "node_mask = np.full(mesh1d.node_x.size, True)"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "#### Compute multiple contacts"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 7,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [
    {
     "data": {
      "image/png": "",
      "text/plain": [
       "<Figure size 640x480 with 1 Axes>"
      ]
     },
     "metadata": {},
     "output_type": "display_data"
    }
   ],
   "source": [
    "mk.contacts_compute_multiple(node_mask)\n",
    "mesh1d_output_0 = mk.mesh1d_get()\n",
    "mesh2d_output_0 = mk.mesh2d_get()\n",
    "contacts_output_0 = mk.contacts_get()\n",
    "plot_mesh_and_contacts(mesh1d_output_0, mesh2d_output_0, contacts_output_0)"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "#### Compute single contacts"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 8,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [
    {
     "data": {
      "image/png": "",
      "text/plain": [
       "<Figure size 640x480 with 1 Axes>"
      ]
     },
     "metadata": {},
     "output_type": "display_data"
    }
   ],
   "source": [
    "x_coordinates = np.array([0.0, 100.0, 100.0, 0.0, 0.0], dtype=np.double)\n",
    "y_coordinates = np.array([0.0, 0.0, 100.0, 100.0, 0.0], dtype=np.double)\n",
    "area_selection = GeometryList(x_coordinates, y_coordinates)\n",
    "mk.contacts_compute_single(node_mask, area_selection, projection_factor=0.0)\n",
    "mesh1d_output_0 = mk.mesh1d_get()\n",
    "mesh2d_output_0 = mk.mesh2d_get()\n",
    "contacts_output_0 = mk.contacts_get()\n",
    "plot_mesh_and_contacts(mesh1d_output_0, mesh2d_output_0, contacts_output_0)"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "#### Contacts compute with points"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 9,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [
    {
     "data": {
      "image/png": "",
      "text/plain": [
       "<Figure size 640x480 with 1 Axes>"
      ]
     },
     "metadata": {},
     "output_type": "display_data"
    }
   ],
   "source": [
    "x_coordinates = np.array([10.000001], dtype=np.double)\n",
    "y_coordinates = np.array([5.0], dtype=np.double)\n",
    "point_cloud = GeometryList(x_coordinates, y_coordinates)\n",
    "\n",
    "mk.contacts_compute_with_points(node_mask, point_cloud)\n",
    "mesh1d_output_0 = mk.mesh1d_get()\n",
    "mesh2d_output_0 = mk.mesh2d_get()\n",
    "contacts_output_0 = mk.contacts_get()\n",
    "plot_mesh_and_contacts(mesh1d_output_0, mesh2d_output_0, contacts_output_0)"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "### Compute boundary"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 10,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [
    {
     "data": {
      "image/png": "",
      "text/plain": [
       "<Figure size 640x480 with 1 Axes>"
      ]
     },
     "metadata": {},
     "output_type": "display_data"
    }
   ],
   "source": [
    "mk.contacts_compute_boundary(node_mask, search_radius=50.0)\n",
    "mesh1d_output_0 = mk.mesh1d_get()\n",
    "mesh2d_output_0 = mk.mesh2d_get()\n",
    "contacts_output_0 = mk.contacts_get()\n",
    "plot_mesh_and_contacts(mesh1d_output_0, mesh2d_output_0, contacts_output_0)"
   ]
  },
